These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, avocado, apple, mango
1. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
3. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | papaya | avocado | apple | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, 7up, sprite, milk
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | almond-milk | milk | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, video-games, woodworking, traveling
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | chess | woodworking | video-games | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, fantasy, thriller, drama
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | sports | drama | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
