2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | skiing | lacrosse | biathlon | cycling |

