.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, potato, cabbage, papaya
1. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
2. the person eating potato is between the person eating cherry and the person eating papaya##2
3. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
4. the person eating cherry is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | papaya | potato | cherry | cabbage |

