2. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2  |      3       |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | fantasy | family | crime |

