.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, trance, techno, reggae
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
4. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | techno | trance | gospel | reggae |

 